{"tid":1834024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"農曆新年禁忌盤點","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T08:04:49.000Z","uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42662be584e63ae75fa76a72086344d6ea8e2136","tid":1834024,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:04:49.000Z","msg":"五、避免看醫生、吃藥<br />\n據說過年期間就在吃藥看醫生，新的一年可能都會不健康，不過沒人會希望過年的假期都耗在醫院等著看診吧，當然是有必要才會前往；至於吃藥，現代人多了很多如高血壓等慢性疾病，藥都是要天天吃的，這個禁忌我們只能盡量避免囉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.skyscanner.com.tw/news/chinese-new-year-custom-taboos-201712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skyscanner.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fchinese-new-year-custom-taboos-201712&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=42c27f4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.skyscanner.com.tw/news/chinese-new-year-custom-taboos-201712</a>"}]}